name: 2014 Photography Calendar
description:
Our photography calendar features 12 beautifully designed months that sits in a clear easel (easel included). Lovely to keep on your desk or to use as a gift. We used 100% Recyclable Paper (post consumer) and archival ink. 

Our desktop calendars measure 4.25" x 5.5" and come with a little 5" clear easel to sit on. 

These make great stocking stuffers. Please let us know if you need this as a gift because we do offer gift tags and pretty boxes too!

***Proudly made in USA***
Eco-Statement: The paper mill we work with is based in the US and is eco-friendly, providing hydro and wind power to their mill, generally giving back to the grid. The paper is also FSC certified and has no bleach or harsh environment-unfriendly chemicals. The printer that we use is based out of the DC metro area and is environmentally conscious along with FSC certifications.

name: Greeting Cards - Mixed Box Set
description:
Our photo greeting cards are digitally printed onto a fine cotton paper, with a beautiful matching envelope. Use it to say thank you to a friend, a special note or give our box set as a gift. 

Greeting Card Information:
Cards are an A2 size (5.5" x 4.125") with matching A2 envelopes
10 cards to a pack
An assortment of our photography

If you would like higher quantities please feel free to email {heather@sdinvites.com} us and we would be more than happy to help.
